This paper discusses the robustness of deep neural networks, which is a topic that is relevant to several sub-fields of computer science. The most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), as the paper evaluates the robustness of recurrent neural networks. Other likely sub-categories include cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
